title: SBB - SBB 1 (1974; 2004) [APE]
description:
SBB - SBB 1 (1974; 2004)

A Box Set containing 22 studio & live albums by SBB (almost all in their discography), released till year 2004. The last 2 albums are compilations of rare & unreleased tracks with guest musicians such as Tomasz Stanko. Those 2 CD's are available ONLY in the box set (while the remaining 20 albums are also sold separately). Almost all albums include various bonus tracks (there are over 60 in the whole set). Limited edition (only 1000 copies).
